trans-unit.source: Specifies the layout of items in a list control.
trans-unit.target: List 컨트롤에 있는 항목의 레이아웃을 지정합니다.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.RepeatLayout> enumeration represents the different layout options for a list control.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.RepeatLayout> 열거형은 목록 컨트롤에 대 한 다른 레이아웃 옵션을 나타냅니다.

trans-unit.source: Items are displayed without a table structure.
Rendered markup consists of a <see langword="span" /> element and items are separated by <see langword="br" /> elements.
trans-unit.target: 렌더링된 태그는 <see langword="span" /> 요소로 구성되며 항목은 <see langword="br" /> 요소로 분리됩니다.

trans-unit.source: The following example shows markup that is rendered for a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CheckBoxList> control whose <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CheckBoxList.RepeatLayout%2A> property is set to Flow.
trans-unit.target: 다음 예제에 대 한 렌더링 되는 태그를 보여 줍니다.는 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CheckBoxList> 컨트롤 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CheckBoxList.RepeatLayout%2A> 흐름에 속성이 설정 되어 있습니다.

trans-unit.source: Items are displayed without a table structure.
Rendered markup consists of an <see langword="ol" /> element that contains <see langword="li" /> elements.
trans-unit.target: 렌더링된 태그는 <see langword="ol" /> 요소가 포함된 <see langword="li" /> 요소로 구성됩니다.

trans-unit.source: The following example shows markup that is rendered for a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CheckBoxList> control whose <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CheckBoxList.RepeatLayout%2A> property is set to OrderedList.
trans-unit.target: 다음 예제에 대해 렌더링 되는 태그는 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CheckBoxList> 컨트롤 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CheckBoxList.RepeatLayout%2A> OrderedList 속성입니다.

trans-unit.source: This field is new as of ASP.NET 4 and is a valid option only for the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CheckBoxList> and <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.RadioButtonList> controls.
trans-unit.target: 이 필드는 ASP.NET 4 기준 새로운 이며에 대해서만 유효한 옵션은 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CheckBoxList> 및 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.RadioButtonList> 컨트롤입니다.

trans-unit.source: Items are displayed in a table.

The following example shows markup that is rendered for a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CheckBoxList> control whose <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CheckBoxList.RepeatLayout%2A> property is set to Table.
trans-unit.target: 다음 예제에서는 태그에 대해 렌더링 되는 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CheckBoxList> 컨트롤 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CheckBoxList.RepeatLayout%2A> 테이블 속성입니다.

trans-unit.source: This option causes the control to render HTML that might not conform to accessibility standards.
trans-unit.target: 이 옵션을 사용 하면 컨트롤이 내게 필요한 옵션 표준 준수 하지 않을 수 있는 HTML을 렌더링 하도록 합니다.

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [Accessibility in Visual Studio and ASP.NET](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/7e3ce9c4-6b7d-4fb1-94b5-72cf2a44fe13).
trans-unit.target: 자세한 내용은 참조 [Visual Studio 및 ASP.NET의 내게 필요한 옵션](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/7e3ce9c4-6b7d-4fb1-94b5-72cf2a44fe13)합니다.

trans-unit.source: Items are displayed without a table structure.
Rendered markup consists of a <see langword="ul" /> element that contains <see langword="li" /> elements.
trans-unit.target: 렌더링된 태그는 <see langword="ul" /> 요소가 포함된 <see langword="li" /> 요소로 구성됩니다.

trans-unit.source: The following example shows markup that is rendered for a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CheckBoxList> control whose <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CheckBoxList.RepeatLayout%2A> property is set to UnorderedList.
trans-unit.target: 다음 예제에 대해 렌더링 되는 태그는 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CheckBoxList> 컨트롤 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CheckBoxList.RepeatLayout%2A> UnorderedList 속성입니다.

trans-unit.source: This field is new as of ASP.NET 4 and is a valid option only for the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CheckBoxList> and <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.RadioButtonList> controls.
trans-unit.target: 이 필드는 ASP.NET 4 기준 새로운 이며에 대해서만 유효한 옵션은 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CheckBoxList> 및 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.RadioButtonList> 컨트롤입니다.
